}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== Per '''catc''''s source, this device... *has a USB ID of 0423:000c (0x0423, 0xC) *which is labeled as using NetMate II
Specifications, as provided by '''Belkin''''s manual, follow... *Data transfer rate: Can exceed 6Mbps (depending on the computer, OS, and communication protocol) *Memory size: 32K (8-bit SRAM for IO data buffers), 1024-bit NVRAM for configuration settings *Power requirement: 5V, 200mA *Dimensions: 4.25" x 3.75" x 1.25" *Weight: 3.9 oz
